#: index.docbook:580
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<shortcut><keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>C</keycap></keycombo> </"
"shortcut> <guimenu>Edit</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Copy Map</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<shortcut><keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>C</keycap></keycombo> </"
"shortcut> <guimenu>सम्पादन</guimenu> <guimenuitem>नक्शा प्रतिलिपिकृत्य</"
"guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:584
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<action>Copies</action> a screenshot of &marble;'s map to the global "
"clipboard."
msgstr ""
"<action>&marble;इत्यस्य मानचित्रस्य स्क्रीनशॉट् वैश्विकक्लिप्बोर्ड् प्रति प्रतिलिपयति</"
"action> ।"

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:588
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guimenu>Edit</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Copy Coordinates</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<guimenu>सम्पादनं</guimenu> <guimenuitem>निर्देशाङ्कानां प्रतिलिपिः</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:591
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<action>Copies</action> the current coordinates to the global clipboard."
msgstr "<action>वर्तमाननिर्देशाङ्कान् वैश्विकक्लिप्बोर्ड् प्रति प्रतिलिपयति</action> ।"

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:595
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<shortcut><keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>E</keycap></keycombo> </"
"shortcut> <guimenu>Edit</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Edit Map...</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<shortcut><keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>E</keycap></keycombo> </"
"shortcut> <guimenu>सम्पादनं</guimenu> <guimenuitem>नक्शा सम्पादयतु...</"
"guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:599
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<action>Allows</action> you to open the current map in the external map "
"editor. The current version supports <application>Potlatch</application> (in "
"a web browser), <application>Merkaartor</application> and <application>JOSM</"
"application> map editors."
msgstr ""
"<action>बाह्यमानचित्रसम्पादके वर्तमाननक्शं उद्घाटयितुं</action> अनुमतिं ददाति । "
"वर्तमानसंस्करणं <application>Potlatch</application> (जालपुटे), "
"<application>Merkaartor</application> तथा <application>JOSM</application> "
"मानचित्रसम्पादकानां समर्थनं करोति ।"

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:603
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<shortcut><keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;&Shift;<keycap>R</keycap></"
"keycombo> </shortcut> <guimenu>Edit</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Record Movie</"
"guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<shortcut><keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;&Shift;<keycap>R</keycap></"
"keycombo> </shortcut> <guimenu>सम्पादनं</guimenu> <guimenuitem>चलचित्रस्य "
"अभिलेखः</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:607
#, no-c-format
msgid "<action>Records</action> a movie with &marble;."
msgstr "<action>अभिलेखयति</action> &marble;."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:611
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guimenu>Edit</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Stop Recording</guimenuitem>"
msgstr "<guimenu>सम्पादनं</guimenu> <guimenuitem>अभिलेखनं स्थगयतु</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:614
#, no-c-format
msgid "<action>Stops</action> the current recording of movie."
msgstr "<action>चलच्चित्रस्य वर्तमानं रिकार्डिङ्ग् स्थगयति</action> ।"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:620
#, no-c-format
msgid "The View Menu"
msgstr "दृश्य मेनू इति"

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:624
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guimenu>View</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Current Location</guimenuitem>"
msgstr "<guimenu>दृश्य</guimenu> <guimenuitem>वर्तमानस्थान</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:627
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<action>Toggle</action> the display of the location page in the left panel. "
"If a GPS device is connected with your computer, &marble; displays longitude "
"and latitude of your current location."
msgstr ""
"<action>Toggle</action> वामपटलस्य स्थानपृष्ठस्य प्रदर्शनं कुर्वन्तु । यदि भवतः सङ्गणकेन सह "
"GPS-यन्त्रं सम्बद्धं भवति तर्हि &marble; भवतः वर्तमानस्थानस्य देशान्तरं अक्षांशं च प्रदर्शयति ।"

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:631
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guimenu>View</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Crosshairs</guimenuitem>"
msgstr "<guimenu>दृश्य</guimenu> <guimenuitem>क्रॉसशेयर</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:634
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<action>Toggle</action> the display of a simple crosshair in the center of "
"the map."
msgstr "<action>Toggle</action> नक्शे केन्द्रे सरलस्य क्रॉसहेयरस्य प्रदर्शनं ।"

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:638
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<shortcut><keycap>F5</keycap></shortcut> <guimenu>View</guimenu> "
"<guimenuitem>Refresh</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<shortcut><keycap>F5</keycap></shortcut> <guimenu>दृश्य</guimenu> "
"<guimenuitem>ताजगीकृत्य</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:642
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The currently visible part of the map is downloaded again and refreshed on "
"the screen."
msgstr "नक्शायाः सम्प्रति दृश्यमानः भागः पुनः अवतरणं कृत्वा पटले ताजगीकृतः भवति ।"

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:646
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guimenu>View</guimenu> <guisubmenu>Info Boxes</guisubmenu>"
msgstr "<guimenu>दृश्य</guimenu> <guimenu>सूचनापेटिकाः</guimenu>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:649
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"In this submenu you can to lock the position of the infoboxes and show or "
"hide the plugins you have enabled in the <link linkend=\"configplugins"
"\">Plugins</link> page of &marble;s configuration dialog."
msgstr ""
"अस्मिन् उपमेनूमध्ये भवान् infoboxes इत्यस्य स्थानं लॉक् कर्तुं शक्नोति तथा च भवता सक्षमकृतानि "
"प्लगिन्स् दर्शयितुं वा गोपयितुं वा शक्नोति<link linkend=\"configplugins\"> प्लगिन्स्</"
"link> &amp;marble;s विन्याससंवादस्य पृष्ठम् ।"

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:653
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guimenu>View</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Online Services</guimenuitem>"
msgstr "<guimenu>दृश्य</guimenu> <guimenuitem>अनलाइनसेवा</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:656
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The <guimenuitem>Wikipedia</guimenuitem> plugin displays georeferenced "
"Wikipedia articles as an icon on the map. A click onto the icon launches a "
"browser window that displays the referenced site. The data is provided "
"through a webservice via GeoNames.org. Likewise a <guimenuitem>Photos</"
"guimenuitem> plugin currently provides photos via the FlickR photo sharing "
"site."
msgstr ""
"<guimenuitem>विकिपीडिया</guimenuitem> प्लगिन् भूसन्दर्भयुक्तान् विकिपीडियालेखान् "
"मानचित्रे चिह्नरूपेण प्रदर्शयति । चिह्नस्य उपरि क्लिक् कृत्वा ब्राउजर् विण्डो प्रारभ्यते यत् "
"सन्दर्भितं साइट् प्रदर्शयति । दत्तांशः GeoNames.org मार्गेण जालसेवाद्वारा प्रदत्तः भवति । "
"तथैव <guimenuitem>Photos</guimenuitem> प्लगिन् सम्प्रति FlickR फोटोसाझेदारीस्थलेन "
"छायाचित्रं प्रदाति ।"

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:660
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guimenu>View</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Clouds</guimenuitem>"
msgstr "<guimenu>दृश्य</guimenu> <guimenuitem>मेघाः</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:663
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<action>Show</action> real-time cloud cover. A real-time cloud map that gets "
"updated every 3 hours. It uses GOES, METEOSAT, and GMS satellite imagery "
"downloaded from the Geostationary Satellite Imagery page at Dundee "
"University. Credits: Hari Nair, Xplanet Project."
msgstr ""
"<action>प्रदर्शन</action> वास्तविकसमये मेघावरणम् । वास्तविकसमयस्य मेघनक्शा यः प्रत्येकं ३ "
"घण्टेषु अद्यतनं भवति । अस्मिन् डण्डी विश्वविद्यालये Geostationary Satellite Imagery "
"पृष्ठात् डाउनलोड् कृतानि GOES, METEOSAT, GMS उपग्रहप्रतिमाः उपयुज्यन्ते । श्रेयः - हरि "
"नायर, Xplanet परियोजना।"

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:667
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guimenu>View</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Atmosphere</guimenuitem>"
msgstr "<guimenu>दृश्य</guimenu> <guimenuitem>वातावरण</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:670
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<action>Show</action> the diffuse reflection of the atmosphere around the "
"Earth."
msgstr "<action>दर्श</action> पृथिव्याः परितः वायुमण्डलस्य प्रसारितप्रतिबिम्बम् ।"

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:674
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guimenu>View</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Stars</guimenuitem>"
msgstr "<guimenu>दृश्य</guimenu> <guimenuitem>तारकाः</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:677
#, no-c-format
msgid "<action>Show</action> the star map as seen from the Solar System."
msgstr "<action>सौरमण्डलात् यथा दृश्यते तथा तारा मानचित्रं दर्शयतु</action> ।"

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:681
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guimenu>View</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Sun Control...</guimenuitem>"
msgstr "<guimenu>दृश्य</guimenu> <guimenuitem>सूर्यनियन्त्रण...</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:684
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<action>Displays</action> the <guilabel>Sun Control</guilabel> where you can "
"set the <guilabel>Sun Shading</guilabel> and center the map on subsolar "
"point position."
msgstr ""
"<action> <guilabel>Sun Control</guilabel> इति प्रदर्शयति</action> यत्र भवान् "
"<guilabel>Sun Shading</guilabel> सेट् कर्तुं शक्नोति तथा च मानचित्रं उपसौरबिन्दुस्थाने "
"केन्द्रीक्रियितुं शक्नोति ।"

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:688
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guimenu>View</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Time Control...</guimenuitem>"
msgstr "<guimenu>दृश्य</guimenu> <guimenuitem>समयनियन्त्रण...</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:691
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<action>Displays</action> the <guilabel>Time Control</guilabel> dialog where "
"you can set date and time and the simulation time speed."
msgstr ""
"<action> <guilabel>समयनियन्त्रण</guilabel> संवादं प्रदर्शयति</action> यत्र भवान् "
"तिथिं समयं च अनुकरणसमयवेगं च सेट् कर्तुं शक्नोति ।"

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:695
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guimenu>View</guimenu> <guisubmenu>Eclipses in <replaceable>year</"
"replaceable></guisubmenu>"
msgstr ""
"<guimenu>द्रष्टव्यम्</guimenu> <guisubmenu><replaceable>वर्षे</replaceable></"
"guisubmenu> ग्रहणं करोति"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:698
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<action>Displays</action> the list of the eclipses for the year chosen using "
"<menuchoice><guimenu>View</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Browse Eclipses...</"
"guimenuitem></menuchoice> menu item."
msgstr ""
"<action> <menuchoice><guimenu>दृश्य</guimenu> <guimenuitem>ग्रहणानि ब्राउज् "
"कुर्वन्तु...</guimenuitem></menuchoice> मेनू-वस्तुनः उपयोगेन चयनितवर्षस्य ग्रहणानां सूचीं "
"प्रदर्शयति</action> ।"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:700 index.docbook:709
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This menu item will be shown only when <link linkend=\"eclipsesplugin"
"\">Eclipses</link> plugin is enabled."
msgstr ""
"इदं मेन्यू-वस्तु केवलं तदा एव दर्शितं भविष्यति यदा<link linkend=\"eclipsesplugin\"> "
"ग्रहणानि</link> प्लगिन् सक्षमम् अस्ति ।"

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:704
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guimenu>View</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Browse Eclipses...</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<guimenu>द्रष्टव्यम्</guimenu> <guimenuitem>ग्रहणानि ब्राउज् कुर्वन्तु...</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:707
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<action>Displays</action> the <guilabel>Eclipse Browser</guilabel> dialog "
"where you can set the year to show eclipses for, open plugin settings "
"dialog, view data on eclipse start, end, type and magnitude. Choose some "
"eclipse item from the list and press the <guibutton>Go To Selected Eclipse</"
"guibutton> to view the location of the eclipse on the globe."
msgstr ""
"<action> <guilabel>Eclipse Browser</guilabel> संवादं प्रदर्शयति</action> यत्र "
"भवान् ग्रहणं दर्शयितुं वर्षं सेट् कर्तुं शक्नोति, प्लगिन् सेटिंग्स् संवादं उद्घाटयितुं, ग्रहणस्य "
"आरम्भस्य, समाप्तेः, प्रकारस्य, परिमाणस्य च दत्तांशं द्रष्टुं शक्नोति सूचीतः किञ्चित् ग्रहण-वस्तु "
"चित्वा <guibutton>Go To Selected Eclipse</guibutton> इति नुदन्तु, येन भूमण्डले "
"ग्रहणस्य स्थानं द्रष्टुं शक्यते ।"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:715
#, no-c-format
msgid "The Bookmarks Menu"
msgstr "बुकमार्क मेनू इति"

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:718
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<shortcut><keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>B</keycap></keycombo> </"
"shortcut> <guimenu>Bookmarks</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Add Bookmark...</"
"guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<shortcut><keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>B</keycap></keycombo> </"
"shortcut> <guimenu>पुस्तकचिह्नानि</guimenu> <guimenuitem>पुस्तकचिह्नं योजयतु...</"
"guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:722
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<action>Open the <guilabel>Edit Bookmark</guilabel> dialog</action> to "
"manage a bookmark."
msgstr ""
"<action>पुस्तकचिह्नं प्रबन्धयितुं <guilabel>पुस्तकचिह्नं सम्पादयतु</guilabel> संवादं</"
"action> उद्घाटयन्तु ।"

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:726
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guimenu>Bookmarks</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Show Bookmarks</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<guimenu>पुस्तकचिह्नानि</guimenu> <guimenuitem>पुस्तकचिह्नानि दर्शयतु</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:729
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"A check box for <action>enable the bookmarks visualization on the map.</"
"action>"
msgstr "<action>नक्शे पुस्तकचिह्नदृश्यीकरणं सक्षमं कुर्वन्तु इति चेकबॉक्सः ।</action>"

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:733
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guimenu>Bookmarks</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Set Home Location</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<guimenu>पुस्तकचिह्नानि</guimenu> <guimenuitem>गृहस्थानं सेट् कुर्वन्तु</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: action
#: index.docbook:736
#, no-c-format
msgid "Set the current position as your house."
msgstr "वर्तमानस्थानं भवतः गृहरूपेण सेट् कुर्वन्तु।"

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:740
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guimenu>Bookmarks</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Manage Bookmarks...</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<guimenu>पुस्तकचिह्नानि</guimenu> <guimenuitem>पुस्तकचिह्नानि प्रबन्धयन्तु...</"
"guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:743
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<action>Open the <guilabel>Manage Bookmarks</guilabel> dialog</action> to "
"manage all bookmarks."
msgstr ""
"<action>सर्वं पुस्तकचिह्नं प्रबन्धयितुं <guilabel>पुस्तकचिह्नं प्रबन्धयतु</guilabel> संवादं</"
"action> उद्घाटयन्तु ।"

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:747
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guimenu>Bookmarks</guimenu> <guisubmenu>Default</guisubmenu>"
msgstr "<guimenu>पुस्तकचिह्नानि</guimenu> <guisubmenu>पूर्वनिर्धारित</guisubmenu>"

#. Tag: action
#: index.docbook:750
#, no-c-format
msgid "This submenu shows your default locations."
msgstr "एतत् उपमेनू भवतः पूर्वनिर्धारितस्थानानि दर्शयति ।"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:756
#, no-c-format
msgid "The Settings Menu"
msgstr "सेटिंग्स् मेन्यू इति"

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:760
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guimenu>Settings</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Show Toolbar</guimenuitem>"
msgstr "<guimenu>सेटिंग्स्</guimenu> <guimenuitem>उपकरणपट्टिकां दर्शयतु</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:763
#, no-c-format
msgid "<action>Toggle</action> the display of the toolbar."
msgstr "<action>Toggle</action> इति साधनपट्टिकायाः प्रदर्शनं कुर्वन्तु ।"

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:767
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guimenu>Settings</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Show Statusbar</guimenuitem>"
msgstr "<guimenu>सेटिंग्स्</guimenu> <guimenuitem>स्थितिपट्टिकां दर्शयतु</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:770
#, no-c-format
msgid "<action>Toggle</action> the display of the status bar."
msgstr "<action>Toggle</action> स्थितिपट्टिकायाः प्रदर्शनं कुर्वन्तु ।"

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:774
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guimenu>Settings</guimenu> <guisubmenu>Panels</guisubmenu>"
msgstr "<guimenu>सेटिंग्स्</guimenu> <guisubmenu>पैनल्स्</guisubmenu>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:777
#, no-c-format
msgid "<action>Toggle</action> the display of the &marble; panels."
msgstr "<action>Toggle</action> इत्यस्य प्रदर्शनं &marble; फलकम् ।"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:779
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"You can make &marble; hide all panels or show them by selecting the "
"<menuchoice><guimenu>Settings</guimenu> <guisubmenu>Panels</guisubmenu> "
"<guimenuitem>Hide All Panels/Show All Panels</guimenuitem></menuchoice> menu "
"item or pressing <keycap>F9</keycap> key on your keyboard."
msgstr ""
"भवन्तः &marble; सर्वाणि पटलानि गोपयन्तु अथवा <menuchoice><guimenu>सेटिंग्स्</"
"guimenu> <guisubmenu>पैनल्स्</guisubmenu> <guimenuitem>सर्वपटलानि गोपयन्तु/"
"सर्वपटलानि दर्शयतु</guimenuitem></menuchoice> मेनू-वस्तुं चित्वा अथवा तान् दर्शयन्तु "
"<keycap>F9</keycap> कीलं भवतः कीबोर्ड् मध्ये ।"

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:783
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guimenu>Settings</guimenu> <guisubmenu>View Size</guisubmenu>"
msgstr "<guimenu>सेटिंग्स्</guimenu> <guisubmenu>आकारं पश्यन्तु</guisubmenu>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:786
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<action>Switches between various sizes of &marble; map area.</action> You "
"can choose one of the sizes that are suitable for capturing frames for "
"screencast or keep &marble; map area resizable (<guimenuitem>Default "
"(resizable)</guimenuitem> item)."
msgstr ""
"<action>&marble; map area.</action> भवान् स्क्रीनकास्ट् कृते फ्रेम्स् गृहीतुं उपयुक्तेषु आकारेषु "
"एकं चिन्वतु अथवा &marble; नक्शाक्षेत्रस्य आकारः परिवर्तनीयः "
"(<guimenuitem>पूर्वनिर्धारितः (आकारः आकारः)</guimenuitem> मदः) ।"

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:790
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<shortcut><keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;&Shift;<keycap>F</keycap></"
"keycombo> </shortcut> <guimenu>Settings</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Full Screen "
"Mode</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<shortcut><keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;&Shift;<keycap>F</keycap></"
"keycombo> </shortcut> <guimenu>सेटिंग्स्</guimenu> <guimenuitem>पूर्णपर्दे मोड</"
"guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:794
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<action>Switches between normal view and full screen view.</action> In full "
"screen view, the titlebar is hidden and the actual application window is "
"resized to the entire screen."
msgstr ""
"<action>सामान्यदृश्यस्य पूर्णपर्देदृश्यस्य च मध्ये परिवर्तनं करोति ।</action> पूर्णपर्दे दृश्ये "
"शीर्षकपट्टिका निगूढा भवति तथा च वास्तविकस्य अनुप्रयोगविण्डो इत्यस्य आकारः सम्पूर्णपर्दे "
"परिवर्तितः भवति"

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:798
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guimenu>Settings</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Configure &marble; Virtual Globe..."
"</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<guimenu>सेटिंग्स्</guimenu> <guimenuitem>विन्यस्तं कुर्वन्तु &marble; आभासी ग्लोब…</"
"guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:801
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<action>Display</action> the <link linkend=\"configure\">&marble; "
"configuration</link> dialog."
msgstr ""
"<action>प्रदर्शन</action> the<link linkend=\"configure\"> &amp; संगमरमर; "
"विन्यासः</link> संवादः ।"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:809
#, no-c-format
msgid "The Help Menu"
msgstr "सहायता मेनू"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:811
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&marble; has the common &kde; <guimenu>Help</guimenu> menu item, for more "
"information read the section about the <ulink url=\"help:/fundamentals/menus."
"html#menus-help\">Help Menu</ulink> of the &kde; Fundamentals."
msgstr ""
"& संगमरमर; सामान्यं &kde; <guimenu>सहायता</guimenu> मेनू-वस्तु, अधिकसूचनार्थं &kde; "
"मौलिकता।"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:818
#, no-c-format
msgid "Configuring &marble;"
msgstr "विन्यस्तं कुर्वन् & marble;"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:821
#, no-c-format
msgid "View Configuration"
msgstr "विन्यासः पश्यन्तु"

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: index.docbook:824
#, no-c-format
msgid "<screeninfo>The View configuration dialog</screeninfo>"
msgstr "<screeninfo>दृश्यविन्याससंवादः</screeninfo>"

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:827
#, no-c-format
msgid "<phrase>The View configuration dialog</phrase>"
msgstr "<phrase>दृश्यविन्याससंवादः</phrase>"

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:833
#, no-c-format
msgid "Distance:"
msgstr "दूरी:"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:834
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The unit that gets used to measure altitude, lengths and distances (&eg; km, "
"mi, ft)."
msgstr "ऊर्ध्वतां, दीर्घतां, दूरं च (&eg; km, mi, ft) मापनार्थं यः एककः अभ्यस्तः भवति ।"

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:838
#, no-c-format
msgid "Angle:"
msgstr "कोण:"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:839
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Specifies the notation of angles in coordinates: By default the Degree-"
"Minute-Second notation (&eg; 54°30'00\" ) gets used. As an alternative you "
"can choose decimal degrees (&eg; 54.5°)."
msgstr ""
"निर्देशाङ्केषु कोणानां संकेतनं निर्दिशति: पूर्वनिर्धारितरूपेण Degree-Minute-Second संकेतनस्य "
"(&eg; 54°30'00\" ) उपयोगः भवति । विकल्परूपेण भवान् दशमलव-अङ्कान् (&eg; 54.5°) "
"चिन्वितुं शक्नोति"

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:843
#, no-c-format
msgid "Still image:"
msgstr "स्थिरचित्रम् :"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:844
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Specifies the map quality that gets displayed while there is no user input. "
"Usually this allows for high map quality as speed is no concern."
msgstr ""
"उपयोक्तृनिवेशः नास्ति चेत् प्रदर्शितं भवति इति नक्शागुणवत्तां निर्दिशति । सामान्यतया एतेन "
"उच्चमानचित्रगुणवत्ता भवति यतः गतिः चिन्ता नास्ति ।"

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:848
#, no-c-format
msgid "During animations:"
msgstr "एनिमेशनस्य समये :"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:849
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Specifies the map quality that gets displayed during map animations (&eg; "
"while dragging the globe). Especially on slow machines it is advisable to "
"set this option to <guilabel>Low Quality</guilabel> as this will give better "
"speed."
msgstr ""
"नक्शा-सजीवीकरणस्य समये (&उदा. ग्लोबं कर्षन्) प्रदर्शितं भवति इति नक्शागुणवत्तां निर्दिशति । "
"विशेषतः मन्दयन्त्रेषु एतत् विकल्पं <guilabel>Low Quality</guilabel> इति सेट् कर्तुं प्रशस्तं "
"यतः एतेन उत्तमवेगः प्राप्यते ।"

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:858
#, no-c-format
msgid "Default map font:"
msgstr "पूर्वनिर्धारित नक्शा फ़ॉन्टः :"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:859
#, no-c-format
msgid "The default font that gets used on the map."
msgstr "मानचित्रे यः पूर्वनिर्धारितः फ़ॉन्ट् उपयुज्यते ।"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:865
#, no-c-format
msgid "Navigation Configuration"
msgstr "नेविगेशन विन्यास"

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: index.docbook:868
#, no-c-format
msgid "<screeninfo>The Navigation configuration dialog</screeninfo>"
msgstr "<screeninfo>नेविगेशनविन्याससंवादः</screeninfo>"

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:871
#, no-c-format
msgid "<phrase>The Navigation configuration dialog</phrase>"
msgstr "<phrase>Navigation विन्याससंवादः</phrase>"

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:882
#, no-c-format
msgid "Inertial globe rotation"
msgstr "जड भूमण्डल परिभ्रमण"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:883
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"By default &marble; will use kinetic spinning while dragging the map. You "
"can turn this behavior off using this check box."
msgstr ""
"पूर्वनिर्धारितरूपेण &marble; नक्शां कर्षन् गतिज-स्पिनिंग् इत्यस्य उपयोगं करिष्यति । एतत् "
"चेकबॉक्सं उपयुज्य भवान् एतत् व्यवहारं निष्क्रियं कर्तुं शक्नोति ।"

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:887
#, no-c-format
msgid "Animate voyage to the target"
msgstr "लक्ष्यं प्रति यात्रां सजीवं कुर्वन्तु"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:888
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"When searching for a location &marble; can either move instantly to the new "
"location or it can show a travel animation from the previous place to the "
"new place."
msgstr ""
"स्थानं अन्वेष्यमाणे &marble; तत्क्षणमेव नूतनस्थानं गन्तुं शक्नोति अथवा पूर्वस्थानात् नूतनस्थानं "
"प्रति यात्रासजीवचित्रं दर्शयितुं शक्नोति ।"

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:892
#, no-c-format
msgid "Mouse view rotation"
msgstr "मूषकदृश्य परिभ्रमणम्"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:893
#, no-c-format
msgid "The map and mouse movement is aligned while panning."
msgstr "पैनिंग् करणकाले नक्शाः मूषकस्य च गतिः संरेखिता भवति ।"

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:897
#, no-c-format
msgid "On Startup:"
msgstr "प्रारम्भे :"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:898
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"By default &marble; will display the home location immediately after the "
"application has started. As an alternative it can also show the last "
"position that was active when the user left the application."
msgstr ""
"पूर्वनिर्धारितरूपेण &marble; अनुप्रयोगस्य आरम्भस्य तत्क्षणमेव गृहस्थानं प्रदर्शयिष्यति। "
"विकल्परूपेण एतत् अन्तिमस्थानं अपि दर्शयितुं शक्नोति यत् यदा उपयोक्ता अनुप्रयोगं त्यक्तवान् तदा "
"सक्रियः आसीत् ।"

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:902
#, no-c-format
msgid "External editor:"
msgstr "बाह्य सम्पादकः :"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:903
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Here, you can define the default editor for the maps or choose "
"<guilabel>Always ask</guilabel> if &marble; should ask you to choose before "
"starting the external editor."
msgstr ""
"अत्र, भवान् नक्शानां कृते पूर्वनिर्धारितं सम्पादकं परिभाषितुं शक्नोति अथवा <guilabel>Always "
"ask</guilabel> इति चिन्वतु यदि &marble; बाह्यसम्पादकं आरभ्यतुं पूर्वं भवन्तं चयनं कर्तुं "
"पृच्छितव्यम् ।"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:909
#, no-c-format
msgid "Cache &amp; Proxy Configuration"
msgstr "Cache &amp; प्रॉक्सी विन्यासः"

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: index.docbook:912
#, no-c-format
msgid "<screeninfo>The Cache &amp; Proxy configuration dialog</screeninfo>"
msgstr "<screeninfo>संग्रहः &amp; प्रॉक्सी विन्याससंवादः</screeninfo>"

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:915
#, no-c-format
msgid "<phrase>The Cache &amp; Proxy configuration dialog</phrase>"
msgstr "<phrase>संग्रहः &amp; प्रॉक्सी विन्याससंवादः</phrase>"

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:921
#, no-c-format
msgid "Cache"
msgstr "संग्रहणम्"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:922
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"There are two caches being used for &marble;: The <guilabel>Physical memory:"
"</guilabel> which is needed to keep map data in the computer's memory. "
"Increasing the value will make the application more responsive. The "
"<guilabel>Hard disc:</guilabel> memory cache is used by download contents "
"from the Internet (&eg; Wikipedia data or map data). Decrease this value if "
"you want to save space on the hard disc and if high usage of the Internet is "
"not an issue."
msgstr ""
"&marble;: <guilabel>Physical memory:</guilabel> इत्यस्य कृते द्वौ सञ्चयौ उपयुज्यन्ते "
"यत् सङ्गणकस्य स्मृतौ नक्शादत्तांशं स्थापयितुं आवश्यकम् अस्ति । मूल्यं वर्धयित्वा अनुप्रयोगः अधिकं "
"प्रतिक्रियाशीलः भविष्यति । <guilabel>हार्डडिस्क:</guilabel> स्मृतिसञ्चयः अन्तर्जालतः "
"सामग्रीं (&उदा. विकिपीडियादत्तांशः अथवा मानचित्रदत्तांशः) अवतरणं कृत्वा उपयुज्यते । यदि "
"भवान् हार्डडिस्क् मध्ये स्थानं रक्षितुं इच्छति तथा च यदि अन्तर्जालस्य उच्चः उपयोगः समस्या "
"नास्ति तर्हि एतत् मूल्यं न्यूनीकरोतु ।"

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:926
#, no-c-format
msgid "Proxy"
msgstr "प्रॉक्सी"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:927
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Proxy settings for your local intranet. Please leave empty if there is no "
"proxy."
msgstr "भवतः स्थानीय-अन्तर्जालस्य प्रॉक्सी-सेटिंग्स् । कृपया रिक्तं त्यजन्तु यदि प्रॉक्सी नास्ति।"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:933
#, no-c-format
msgid "Date &amp; Time Configuration"
msgstr "तिथि &amp; समय विन्यास"

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: index.docbook:936
#, no-c-format
msgid "<screeninfo>The Date &amp; Time configuration dialog</screeninfo>"
msgstr "<screeninfo>तिथिः &amp; समयविन्याससंवादः</screeninfo>"

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:939
#, no-c-format
msgid "<phrase>The Date &amp; Time configuration dialog</phrase>"
msgstr "<phrase>तिथिः &amp; समयविन्याससंवादः</phrase>"

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:945
#, no-c-format
msgid "Time Zone"
msgstr "समयक्षेत्रम्"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:946
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Here, you can choose a time zone for &marble;: <ulink url=\"https://en."
"wikipedia.org/wiki/Coordinated_Universal_Time\">UTC</ulink>, system time "
"zone or choose custom time zone. The chosen option changes the map view only "
"if the map can show the light conditions on the surface."
msgstr ""
"अत्र, भवान् &marble;: <ulink url=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/"
"Coordinated_Universal_Time\">UTC</ulink>, प्रणालीसमयक्षेत्रं वा इष्टसमयक्षेत्रं चिन्वतु "
"। चयनितः विकल्पः केवलं तदा एव नक्शादृश्यं परिवर्तयति यदा नक्शा पृष्ठे प्रकाशस्य स्थितिं "
"दर्शयितुं शक्नोति ।"

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:950
#, no-c-format
msgid "When &marble; starts"
msgstr "यदा & संगमरवरः; आरभते"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:951
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Here, you can choose the date and time which will be used on &marble; start: "
"system time or the last session time."
msgstr ""
"अत्र, भवान् तिथिं समयं च चिन्वतु यस्य उपयोगः &marble; start: सिस्टम् समयः अथवा अन्तिमः "
"सत्रसमयः।"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:957
#, no-c-format
msgid "Synchronization Configuration"
msgstr "समन्वयन विन्यास"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:959
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&marble; can upload route and bookmark data to <ulink url=\"https://en."
"wikipedia.org/wiki/OwnCloud\">ownCloud</ulink> server and synchronize them "
"between &marble; instances installed on different devices."
msgstr ""
"& संगमरमर; मार्ग-दत्तांशं बुकमार्कं च <ulink url=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/"
"OwnCloud\">ownCloud</ulink> सर्वरे अपलोड् कृत्वा &marble; विभिन्नेषु उपकरणेषु "
"संस्थापितानि उदाहरणानि।"

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: index.docbook:963
#, no-c-format
msgid "<screeninfo>The Synchronization configuration dialog</screeninfo>"
msgstr "<screeninfo>समन्वयनविन्याससंवादः</screeninfo>"

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:966
#, no-c-format
msgid "<phrase>The Synchronization configuration dialog</phrase>"
msgstr "<phrase>समन्वयनविन्याससंवादः</phrase>"

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:972
#, no-c-format
msgid "Enable synchronization"
msgstr "समन्वयनं सक्षमं कुर्वन्तु"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:973
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The synchronization can be enabled or disabled using this item. When the "
"synchronization is enabled you can choose whether to synchronize route and "
"bookmark data using the corresponding check boxes or press the "
"<guibutton>Sync now</guibutton> button to initiate synchronization "
"immediately."
msgstr ""
"एतस्य द्रव्यस्य उपयोगेन समन्वयनं सक्षमं निष्क्रियं वा कर्तुं शक्यते । यदा समन्वयनं सक्षमं भवति "
"तदा भवान् तत्सम्बद्धानां चेकबॉक्सानाम् उपयोगेन मार्गस्य तथा बुकमार्कदत्तांशस्य समन्वयनं कर्तुं "
"शक्नोति वा तत्क्षणमेव समन्वयनं आरभ्य <guibutton>Sync now</guibutton> बटनं नुदतु इति "
"चिन्वतु"

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:977
#, no-c-format
msgid "Credentials"
msgstr "प्रमाणपत्राणि"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:978
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Here, you can enter your ownClowd credentials. More information on ownClowd "
"configuration can be found on the <ulink url=\"https://owncloud.com/"
"\">ownClowd official website</ulink>."
msgstr ""
"अत्र, भवान् स्वस्यClowd प्रमाणपत्रं प्रविष्टुं शक्नोति । ownClowd विन्यासस्य विषये अधिका "
"सूचना <ulink url=\"https://owncloud.com/\">ownClowd आधिकारिकजालस्थले</ulink> "
"इत्यत्र प्राप्यते ।"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:984
#, no-c-format
msgid "Routing Configuration"
msgstr "मार्गनिर्देशनविन्यासः"

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: index.docbook:987
#, no-c-format
msgid "<screeninfo>The Routing configuration dialog</screeninfo>"
msgstr "<screeninfo>मार्गनिर्देशनविन्याससंवादः</screeninfo>"

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:990
#, no-c-format
msgid "<phrase>The Routing configuration dialog</phrase>"
msgstr "<phrase>मार्गनिर्देशनविन्याससंवादः</phrase>"

#. Tag: guibutton
#: index.docbook:996
#, no-c-format
msgid "Add..."
msgstr "संयोजयति..."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:997
#, no-c-format
msgid "Opens a window where you can add a new routing profile."
msgstr "एकं विण्डो उद्घाटयति यत्र भवान् नूतनं मार्गनिर्देशनप्रोफाइलं योजयितुं शक्नोति ।"

#. Tag: guibutton
#: index.docbook:1001
#, no-c-format
msgid "Configure..."
msgstr "विन्यस्तं कुर्वन्तु..."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1002
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Opens a window where the currently selected routing profile can be "
"configured."
msgstr "एकं विण्डो उद्घाटयति यत्र वर्तमानकाले चयनितं मार्गरूपरेखा विन्यस्तुं शक्यते ।"

#. Tag: guibutton
#: index.docbook:1006
#, no-c-format
msgid "Remove"
msgstr "अपाकरोति"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1007
#, no-c-format
msgid "Deletes the selected routing profile."
msgstr "चयनितं मार्गनिर्देशनप्रोफाइलं विलोपयति ।"

#. Tag: guibutton
#: index.docbook:1011
#, no-c-format
msgid "Move Up"
msgstr "उपरि गच्छतु"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1012
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The selected routing profile is moved up one step. It will appear before the "
"one that was previously on top of it."
msgstr ""
"चयनितं मार्गनिर्देशनप्रोफाइलं एकं पदं उपरि गच्छति । तस्य उपरि पूर्वं यत् आसीत् तस्य पुरतः "
"दृश्यते ।"

#. Tag: guibutton
#: index.docbook:1016
#, no-c-format
msgid "Move Down"
msgstr "अधः गच्छतु"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1017
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The selected routing profile is moved down one step. It will appear after "
"the one that was previously below of it."
msgstr ""
"चयनितं मार्गनिर्देशनप्रोफाइलं एकं पदं अधः गच्छति । तस्याधः पूर्वं यत् आसीत् तस्य पश्चात् दृश्यते।"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:1023
#, no-c-format
msgid "Plugins Configuration"
msgstr "प्लगिन्स् विन्यासः"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1025
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The <guilabel>Plugin Configuration</guilabel> widget is the place to "
"activate (or deactivate) Info Boxes, Online Services and other plugins that "
"affect the look of &marble;. Active plugins appear in the <guilabel>View</"
"guilabel> menu where you can toggle their visibility."
msgstr ""
"<guilabel>प्लगिन् विन्यास</guilabel> विजेट् &marble; सक्रियप्लगिन्स् <guilabel>View</"
"guilabel> मेन्यू मध्ये दृश्यन्ते यत्र भवान् तेषां दृश्यतां टॉग्ल् कर्तुं शक्नोति ।"

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: index.docbook:1029
#, no-c-format
msgid "<screeninfo>The Plugins configuration dialog</screeninfo>"
msgstr "<screeninfo>प्लगिन्स् विन्याससंवादः</screeninfo>"

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:1032
#, no-c-format
msgid "<phrase>The Plugins configuration dialog</phrase>"
msgstr "<phrase>प्लगिन्स् विन्याससंवादः</phrase>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1036
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Each plugin can be activated and deactivated using the check box on the "
"left. Some plugins provide further configuration options which are "
"accessible by clicking on the tool icon on the right."
msgstr ""
"प्रत्येकं प्लगिन् वामभागे स्थितस्य चेकबॉक्सस्य उपयोगेन सक्रियीकरणं निष्क्रियं च कर्तुं शक्यते । केचन "
"प्लगिन्स् अधिकानि विन्यासविकल्पानि प्रदास्यन्ति ये दक्षिणतः टूल् चिह्नं क्लिक् कृत्वा सुलभाः "
"भवन्ति ।"

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:1041
#, no-c-format
msgid "Amateur Radio Aprs Plugin"
msgstr "शौकिया रेडियो Aprs प्लगइन"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1042
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Retrieves data from the Automatic Packet Reporting System via the Internet, "
"a file or a serial device. The position and status of data senders is "
"displayed in the map and updated in real-time."
msgstr ""
"अन्तर्जालद्वारा, सञ्चिकायाः अथवा क्रमिकयन्त्रस्य माध्यमेन Automatic Packet Reporting "
"System इत्यस्मात् आँकडान् पुनः प्राप्नोति । दत्तांशप्रेषकाणां स्थितिः स्थितिः च मानचित्रे "
"प्रदर्श्यते, वास्तविकसमये च अद्यतनं भवति ।"

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:1046
#, no-c-format
msgid "Annotation"
msgstr "टिप्पणी"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1047
#, no-c-format
msgid "Allows you to add annotations on the maps."
msgstr "नक्शासु टिप्पणीं योजयितुं शक्नोति ।"

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:1051
#, no-c-format
msgid "Atmosphere"
msgstr "वातावरणम्"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1052
#, no-c-format
msgid "Displays atmosphere effects."
msgstr "वातावरणप्रभावं प्रदर्शयति।"

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:1056
#, no-c-format
msgid "Compass"
msgstr "कम्पासः"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1057
#, no-c-format
msgid "Shows a compass in the map."
msgstr "नक्शे कम्पासं दर्शयति।"

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:1061
#, no-c-format
msgid "Coordinate Grid"
msgstr "निर्देशांक जालम्"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1062
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Displays a coordinate grid (you can choose the colors of the grid lines)."
msgstr "एकं निर्देशांकजालं प्रदर्शयति (भवन्तः जालरेखानां वर्णाः चिन्वितुं शक्नुवन्ति) ।"

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:1066
#, no-c-format
msgid "Crosshairs"
msgstr "क्रॉसशेयर"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1067
#, no-c-format
msgid "Enable this to display a small crosshair in the center of the map."
msgstr "नक्शे केन्द्रे लघु क्रॉसहेयर प्रदर्शयितुं एतत् सक्षमं कुर्वन्तु ।"

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:1071
#, no-c-format
msgid "Download Progress Indicator"
msgstr "प्रगति सूचकं डाउनलोड् कुर्वन्तु"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1072
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"A pie chart on top of the map that shows the progress of ongoing downloads."
msgstr "नक्शे उपरि एकः पाई चार्टः यः प्रचलति डाउनलोड्स् इत्यस्य प्रगतिम् दर्शयति ।"

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:1076
#, no-c-format
msgid "Earthquakes"
msgstr "भूकम्पाः"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1077
#, no-c-format
msgid "Displays the earthquake markers on the map."
msgstr "नक्शे भूकम्पचिह्नानि प्रदर्शयति ।"

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:1081
#, no-c-format
msgid "Eclipses"
msgstr "ग्रहणानि"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1082
#, no-c-format
msgid "Displays the data about Solar and Moon eclipses."
msgstr "सौर-चन्द्रग्रहणयोः विषये दत्तांशं प्रदर्शयति ।"

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:1086
#, no-c-format
msgid "Elevation Profile"
msgstr "ऊर्ध्वता प्रोफाइल"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1087
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Displays the elevation profile overlay for <link linkend=\"routing\">the "
"routes on the map</link>."
msgstr ""
"कृते ऊर्ध्वतारूपरेखा आच्छादनं प्रदर्शयति<link linkend=\"routing\"> नक्शे मार्गाः</link> ."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:1091
#, no-c-format
msgid "Elevation Profile Marker"
msgstr "ऊंचाई प्रोफाइल चिह्न"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1092
#, no-c-format
msgid "Marks the current elevation of the elevation profile on the map."
msgstr "मानचित्रे ऊर्ध्वतारूपरेखायाः वर्तमानं ऊर्ध्वतां चिह्नयति ।"

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:1096
#, no-c-format
msgid "GpsInfo"
msgstr "GpsInfo"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1097
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Displays a float item that provides <ulink url=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/"
"wiki/Global_Positioning_System\">GPS</ulink> information."
msgstr ""
"एकं प्लवक-वस्तु प्रदर्शयति यत् <ulink url=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/"
"Global_Positioning_System\">GPS</ulink> सूचनां प्रदाति ।"

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:1101
#, no-c-format
msgid "License"
msgstr "अनुज्ञापत्रम्"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1102
#, no-c-format
msgid "Displays a float item that provides copyright information."
msgstr "एकं float item प्रदर्शयति यत् प्रतिलिपिधर्मस्य सूचनां प्रदाति ।"

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:1106
#, no-c-format
msgid "Measure Tool"
msgstr "मापनसाधनम्"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1107
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The plugin to <link linkend=\"measure-distances\">measure distances between "
"two or more points</link>."
msgstr ""
"प्लगिन् to<link linkend=\"measure-distances\"> द्वयोः वा अधिकयोः बिन्दुयोः मध्ये दूरं "
"मापयन्तु</link> ."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1109
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Displaying of the distance and the bearing between the points can be "
"configured after pressing the tool icon. It is enough to check the "
"corresponding item to make &marble; show the labels or uncheck the item to "
"hide the labels."
msgstr ""
"बिन्दुयोः मध्ये दूरस्य प्रदर्शनं, असरस्य च प्रदर्शनं साधनचिह्नं नुत्वा विन्यस्तुं शक्यते । &marble; "
"लेबल् दर्शयन्तु अथवा लेबल् गोपनार्थं द्रव्यं अनचेक् कुर्वन्तु ।"

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:1113
#, no-c-format
msgid "Navigation"
msgstr "नौकायानम्"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1114
#, no-c-format
msgid "Displays the mouse control to zoom and move as float item on the map."
msgstr "नक्शे float item इति रूपेण zoom कर्तुं move कर्तुं च mouse control प्रदर्शयति ।"

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:1118
#, no-c-format
msgid "OSM Mapper Notes"
msgstr "ओएसएम मैपर नोट्स"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1119
#, no-c-format
msgid "Implementation of geocoding notes."
msgstr "जियोकोडिंग नोट्स् इत्यस्य कार्यान्वयनम्।"

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:1128
#, no-c-format
msgid "OpenDesktop Items"
msgstr "OpenDesktop वस्तूनि"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1129
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Shows <ulink url=\"https://opendesktop.org/\">OpenDesktop</ulink> users' "
"avatars and some extra information about them on the map."
msgstr ""
"<ulink url=\"https://opendesktop.org/\">OpenDesktop</ulink> उपयोक्तृणां अवतारं "
"तेषां विषये च काश्चन अतिरिक्तसूचनाः नक्शे दर्शयति ।"

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:1133
#, no-c-format
msgid "Overview Map"
msgstr "अवलोकन मानचित्र"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1134
#, no-c-format
msgid "This is a float item that provides an overview map."
msgstr "इदं प्लवक-वस्तु अस्ति यत् अवलोकन-नक्शां प्रदाति ।"

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:1138
#, no-c-format
msgid "Photos"
msgstr "फोटो"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1139
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Automatically downloads images from around the world in preference to their "
"popularity."
msgstr "विश्वस्य लोकप्रियतायाः प्राधान्येन विश्वस्य चित्राणि स्वयमेव डाउनलोड् करोति ।"

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:1143
#, no-c-format
msgid "Places"
msgstr "स्थानाः"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1144
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Displays trending <ulink url=\"https://foursquare.com/\">Foursquare</ulink> "
"places."
msgstr ""
"प्रवृत्तियुक्तानि <ulink url=\"https://foursquare.com/\">चतुर्वर्ग</ulink> स्थानानि "
"प्रदर्शयति ।"

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:1148
#, no-c-format
msgid "Position Marker"
msgstr "स्थिति चिह्न"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1149
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Draws a marker at the current <ulink url=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/"
"Global_Positioning_System\">GPS</ulink> position."
msgstr ""
"वर्तमान <ulink url=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Global_Positioning_System"
"\">GPS</ulink> स्थाने एकं चिह्नं आकर्षयति ।"

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:1153
#, no-c-format
msgid "Postal Codes"
msgstr "डाक संहिता"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1154
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Shows <ulink url=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Postal_code\">postal codes</"
"ulink> of the area on the map."
msgstr ""
"नक्शे क्षेत्रस्य <ulink url=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Postal_code"
"\">डाकसङ्केताः</ulink> दर्शयति ।"

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:1158
#, no-c-format
msgid "Routing"
msgstr "मार्गनिर्धारणम्"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1159
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Displays the <link linkend=\"routing\">routing information</link> and "
"navigation controls."
msgstr ""
"प्रदर्शयति<link linkend=\"routing\"> मार्गनिर्देशनसूचना</link> तथा "
"मार्गदर्शननियन्त्रणानि।"

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:1163
#, no-c-format
msgid "Satellites"
msgstr "उपग्रहाः"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1164
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Displays the Earth and other planets natural and artificial satellites and "
"their orbits."
msgstr "पृथिव्याः अन्येषां च ग्रहाणां प्राकृतिककृत्रिम-उपग्रहान् तेषां कक्षां च प्रदर्शयति ।"

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:1168
#, no-c-format
msgid "Scale Bar"
msgstr "स्केल बार"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1169
#, no-c-format
msgid "This is a float item that provides a map scale."
msgstr "इदं प्लवक-वस्तु अस्ति यत् नक्शा-मापदण्डं प्रदाति ।"

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:1173
#, no-c-format
msgid "Speedometer"
msgstr "गतिमापक"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1174
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Displays the current cruising speed. Needs some <ulink url=\"https://en."
"wikipedia.org/wiki/Global_Positioning_System\">GPS</ulink> data."
msgstr ""
"वर्तमानं क्रूजिंग् वेगं प्रदर्शयति । किञ्चित् <ulink url=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/"
"Global_Positioning_System\">GPS</ulink> दत्तांशस्य आवश्यकता अस्ति ।"

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:1178
#, no-c-format
msgid "Stars"
msgstr "तारा"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1179
#, no-c-format
msgid "A plugin that shows the Starry Sky."
msgstr "एकं प्लगिन् यत् Starry Sky दर्शयति ।"

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:1183
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guilabel>Sun</guilabel>"
msgstr "<guilabel>सूर्य</guilabel> इति"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1184
#, no-c-format
msgid "A plugin that shows the Sun."
msgstr "एकं प्लगिन् यत् सूर्यं दर्शयति।"

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:1188
#, no-c-format
msgid "Weather"
msgstr "वातावरणम्‌"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1189
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Downloads current weather information of cities and displays them in the map."
msgstr "नगरानां वर्तमानमौसमसूचनाः डाउनलोड् कृत्वा नक्शे प्रदर्शयति ।"

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:1193
#, no-c-format
msgid "Wikipedia Articles"
msgstr "विकिपीडिया लेख"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1194
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Automatically downloads Wikipedia articles and shows them on the right "
"position on the map."
msgstr "विकिपीडियालेखान् स्वयमेव डाउनलोड् कृत्वा नक्शे सम्यक् स्थाने दर्शयति ।"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:1201
#, no-c-format
msgid "Questions and Answers"
msgstr "प्रश्नोत्तरम्"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1206
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"I cannot see my house on the map / Why should I use &marble; if there is "
"<application>Google Earth</application> already?"
msgstr ""
"अहं नक्शे मम गृहं न पश्यामि / किमर्थं मया &marble; यदि पूर्वमेव <application>Google "
"Earth</application> अस्ति?"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1209
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&marble; aims to be a lightweight fast educational geographical browser that "
"easily runs on any platform that is supported by &Qt;. While higher "
"resolution maps would be nice to have they aren't necessary for every user "
"and every use case (just like you don't use a full blown text processor each "
"time you just need a simple editor). Also notice &marble; is free software "
"and is based on data that can be freely redistributed in the same way that "
"applies to Free Software."
msgstr ""
"& संगमरमर; उद्देश्यं हल्कं द्रुतशैक्षिकं भौगोलिकं ब्राउजर् भवितुम् अर्हति यत् &Qt;द्वारा समर्थितं "
"कस्मिन् अपि मञ्चे सहजतया चाल्यते । यद्यपि उच्चतरसंकल्पनक्शाः भवन्ति चेत् ते प्रत्येकस्य उपयोक्तुः "
"प्रत्येकस्य च उपयोगप्रकरणस्य कृते आवश्यकाः न सन्ति (यथा भवन्तः प्रत्येकं समये पूर्णतया "
"पाठसंसाधकस्य उपयोगं न कुर्वन्ति यत् भवन्तः केवलं सरलसम्पादकस्य आवश्यकतां अनुभवन्ति)। अपि च "
"&marble; मुक्तसॉफ्टवेयरं भवति तथा च मुक्तसॉफ्टवेयरस्य विषये यथा प्रवर्तते तथा स्वतन्त्रतया "
"पुनः वितरितुं शक्यमाणानां दत्तांशानाम् आधारेण भवति ।"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1215
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Why is &marble; so fast although I don't have hardware acceleration "
"enabled? / Why doesn't &marble; run smoothly on my expensive 3D graphics "
"card?"
msgstr ""
"किमर्थं & संगमरवरः; एतावत् शीघ्रं यद्यपि मम हार्डवेयरत्वरणं सक्षमं नास्ति? / किमर्थं न & "
"marble; मम महत् 3D ग्राफिक्स् कार्ड् इत्यत्र सुचारुतया चालयन्तु?"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1218
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Despite depicting the earth as a globe &marble; doesn't make use of any 3D "
"hardware acceleration. This has the advantage of running at a decent speed "
"on any platform and hardware supported by &Qt;. However it has the "
"disadvantage that it doesn't run as smoothly as it could if it used hardware "
"accelerated OpenGL. &marble; just uses plain 2D graphics and therefore "
"requires a graphics adapter that is fast at drawing 2D graphics. We plan to "
"add an optional OpenGL backend in the future."
msgstr ""
"पृथिव्याः भूमण्डलरूपेण चित्रणं कृत्वा अपि &marble; कस्यापि 3D हार्डवेयर त्वरणस्य उपयोगं न "
"करोति । एतस्य लाभः अस्ति यत् &Qt;द्वारा समर्थितस्य कस्मिन् अपि मञ्चे हार्डवेयर्-मध्ये च "
"सभ्यवेगेन चाल्यते । तथापि अस्य दोषः अस्ति यत् यदि हार्डवेयर-त्वरित-OpenGL इत्यस्य उपयोगं "
"कृतवान् तर्हि इदं यथा सुचारुतया न चालयति । & संगमरमर; केवलं साधारणं 2D ग्राफिक्स् उपयुज्यते "
"अतः ग्राफिक्स् एडाप्टरस्य आवश्यकता भवति यत् 2D ग्राफिक्स् आकर्षयितुं द्रुतं भवति । भविष्ये "
"वैकल्पिकं OpenGL पृष्ठभागं योजयितुं योजनामस्ति ।"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1224
#, no-c-format
msgid "Will I ever have to pay for &marble;?"
msgstr "किं मया कदापि &marble;;"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1227
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"No, never. But the authors always welcome feedback. &marble; is licensed "
"under the <ulink url=\"https://www.gnu.org/licenses/licenses.html#LGPL"
"\">LGPL</ulink>, so you will never have to pay for this program."
msgstr ""
"न, कदापि। परन्तु लेखकाः प्रतिक्रियायाः सर्वदा स्वागतं कुर्वन्ति। & संगमरमर; <ulink url="
"\"https://www.gnu.org/licenses/licenses.html#LGPL\">LGPL</ulink> इत्यस्य "
"अन्तर्गतं अनुज्ञापत्रं प्राप्तम् अस्ति, अतः भवद्भिः अस्य कार्यक्रमस्य कृते कदापि धनं दातव्यं न "
"भविष्यति ।"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1233
#, no-c-format
msgid "How can I contribute?"
msgstr "अहं कथं योगदानं दातुं शक्नोमि ?"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1236
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&marble; is not only an application but also a Free Software project. As "
"such it's easy to join: just contact us via the marble-devel mailing list "
"(marble-devel@kde.org)."
msgstr ""
"& संगमरमर; न केवलं अनुप्रयोगः अपितु Free Software परियोजना अपि अस्ति । अतः सम्मिलितुं "
"सुलभम् अस्ति: केवलं marble-devel मेलसूचिकायाः (marble-devel@kde.org) माध्यमेन अस्माभिः "
"सह सम्पर्कं कुर्वन्तु।"

